{"basic_details":{"job_title":"Rajasthan Anganwadi Recruitment 2026 (Bharatpur) - Apply Offline for 55 Anganwadi Worker & Helper Posts","last_updated":"16 Jul 2026","organization_name":"ICDS Bharatpur, Rajasthan (Dept. of Women & Child Development)","post_name":"Anganwadi Karyakarta (Worker), Anganwadi Sahayika (Helper)","total_vacancies":"55 (24 Karyakarta + 31 Sahayika)","application_mode":"Offline, in duplicate, at the concerned CDPO office","job_location":"Bharatpur district, Rajasthan","short_information":"The Office of the Deputy Director, Integrated Child Development Services (ICDS), Bharatpur, under the Rajasthan Government's Department of Women & Child Development, has invited applications for 55 honorary posts of Anganwadi Karyakarta (Worker) and Anganwadi Sahayika (Helper). These vacancies are spread across eight ICDS project offices in Bharatpur district: Bayana, Bharatpur City, Bhusawar, Nadbai, Roopwas, Sewar, Uchhain, and Wair. Eligible local candidates from the concerned Gram Panchayat, ward, or Anganwadi Centre area can submit their applications offline at the respective CDPO office."},"important_dates":{"event":"Date","notification release date":"1 July 2026","application_start_date":"1 July 2026","last_date_to_apply":"30 July 2026, till 4:00 PM"},"application_fee":{},"age_limit":{},"qualification":{"details":"The notification specifies that candidates should belong to the same Gram Panchayat, ward, or Anganwadi Centre catchment area for which the post is vacant. Detailed eligibility criteria, including educational qualification and reservation-related conditions, can be obtained from the concerned CDPO office, as referenced in departmental circular no. 4244 dated 12.01.2023 and letter no. 57871–58286 dated 01.03.2024."},"vacancy_details":[{"Project Office":"Bayana","Karyakarta Posts":"7","Sahayika Posts":"4","Total":"11"},{"Project Office":"Bharatpur City (Nagar Nigam)","Karyakarta Posts":"2","Sahayika Posts":"9","Total":"11"},{"Project Office":"B