ard":"Nagar Nigam Bharatpur","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Jatoli Ghana","post":"Sahayika","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":44,"project_office":"Uchhain","gram_panchayat_ward":"Nagar Palika (New Ward 4,5)","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Uchhain-5","post":"Karyakarta","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":45,"project_office":"Uchhain","gram_panchayat_ward":"Nagar Palika (New Ward 01)","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Uchhain-6","post":"Karyakarta","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":46,"project_office":"Uchhain","gram_panchayat_ward":"Barigha","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Nangla Punthiya","post":"Karyakarta","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":47,"project_office":"Uchhain","gram_panchayat_ward":"Nagar Palika (New Ward 25)","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Uchhain-2","post":"Sahayika","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":48,"project_office":"Uchhain","gram_panchayat_ward":"Mudhera","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Kunder","post":"Sahayika","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":49,"project_office":"Uchhain","gram_panchayat_ward":"Kalyanpur","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Kalyanpur","post":"Sahayika","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":50,"project_office":"Uchhain","gram_panchayat_ward":"Khudasa","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Chandauli","post":"Sahayika","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":51,"project_office":"Uchhain","gram_panchayat_ward":"Barahmafi","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Hirapur","post":"Sahayika","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":52,"project_office":"Uchhain","gram_panchayat_ward":"Aghapur","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Aghapur-1","post":"Sahayika","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":53,"project_office":"Uchhain","gram_panchayat_ward":"Khadera","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Chakramnagar","post":"Sahayika","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":54,"project_office":"Wair","gram_panchayat_ward":"Samraya","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Morda","post":"Sahayika","category":"Unreserved"},{"col_1":55,"project_office":"Wair","gram_panchayat_ward":"Jagjivanpur","anganwadi_centre_village_ward":"Bhaundagaon","post":"Sahayika","category":"Unreserved"}]}]},{"heading":"Eligibility for Anganwadi Karyakarta and Sahayika Posts","text":"The notification specifies that candidates should belong to the same Gram Panchayat, ward, or Anganwadi Centre catchment area for which the post is vacant. Detailed eligibility criteria, including educational qualification and reservation-related conditions, can be obtained from the concerned CDPO office, as referenced in departmental circular no. 4244 dated 12.01.2023 and letter no. 57871–58286 dated 01.03.2024.","tables":[]},{"heading":"How to Apply for ICDS Bharatpur Anganwadi Recruitment 2026","text":"Obtain the detailed vacancy and reservation information from the concerned CDPO (Child Development Project Officer) office for your area. Prepare the application in duplicate (two copies) as required by the notification. Submit both copies in person at the respective CDPO office listed in the Important Links section below. Ensure submission is completed on or before 30 July 2026, by 4:00 PM . If 30 July 2026 is declared a government holiday, the application can be submitted on the next working day.","tables":[]},{"heading":"Important Instructions","text":"Complete details of reserved and unreserved vacancies for each CDPO office are available at the respective office. The detailed vacancy list will also be displayed at the Block/Gram Panchayat and Anganwadi Centre level for wider publicity. Applications must be submitted only to the CDPO office under whose jurisdiction the vacant post falls.","tables":[]},{"heading":"Important Links","text":"","tables":[{"caption":"","rows":[{"cdpo_project_office":"Bayana","email_id":"[email protected]"},{"cdpo_project_office":"Bharatpur City","email_id":"[email protected]"},{"cdpo_project_office":"Bhusawar","email_id":"[email protected]"},{"cdpo_project_office":"Nadbai","email_id":"[email protected]"},{"cdpo_project_office":"Roopwas","email_id":"[email protected]"},{"cdpo_project_office":"Sewar","email_id":"[email protected]"},{"cdpo_project_office":"Uchhain","email_id":"[email protected]"},{"cdpo_project_office":"Wair","email_id":"[email protected]"}]}]},{"heading":"ICDS Bharatpur Anganwadi Worker & Helper Important Links","text":"Official Notification PDF : Click here Official Website: Click here Join Arattai Channel: Click Here Join Telegram Channel: Click Here Join WhatsApp Channel : Click Here Sarkari Result : Click Here Download Mobile App: Click Here","tables":[]}],"faq":[{"question":"Q1. What is the last date to apply for ICDS Bharatpur Anganwadi recruitment 2026?","answer":"The last date to submit the application is 30 July 2026, till 4:00 PM. If this date is a government holiday, the next working day will be considered the last date."},{"question":"Q2. How many vacancies are there in this ICDS Bharatpur notification?","answer":"There are 55 vacancies in total - 24 for Anganwadi Karyakarta and 31 for Anganwadi Sahayika, spread across 8 CDPO project offices in Bharatpur district."},{"question":"Q3. How can I apply for the Anganwadi Karyakarta or Sahayika post in Bharatpur?","answer":"The application must be submitted offline, in duplicate, directly at the concerned CDPO office covering the applicant's Gram Panchayat, ward, or Anganwadi Centre."},{"question":"Q4. How is selection done for these posts?","answer":"Selection is conducted through the Gram Sabha, as per the procedure laid out in departmental circular no. 4244 dated 12.01.2023 and letter no. 57871–58286 dated 01.03.2024."},{"question":"Q5. What is the age limit for these posts?","answer":"Minimum 18 Years and Maximum 35 Years"},{"question":"What is the last date to apply for ICDS Bharatpur Anganwadi recruitment 2026?","answer":"The last date to submit the application is 30 July 2026, till 4:00 PM. If this date is a government holiday, the next working day will be considered the last date."},{"question":"How many vacancies are there in this ICDS Bharatpur notification?","answer":"There are 55 vacancies in total - 24 for Anganwadi Karyakarta and 31 for Anganwadi Sahayika, spread across 8 CDPO project offices in Bharatpur district."},{"question":"How can I apply for the Anganwadi Karyakarta or Sahayika post in Bharatpur?","answer":"The application must be submitted offline, in duplicate, directly at the concerned CDPO office covering the applicant's Gram Panchayat, ward, or Anganwadi Centre."},{"question":"How is selection done for these posts?","answer":"Selection is conducted through the Gram Sabha, as per the procedure laid out in departmental circular no. 4244 dated 12.01.2023 and letter no. 57871–58286 dated 01.03.2024."},{"question":"What is the age limit for these posts?","answer":"Minimum 18 Years and Maximum 35 Years"}],"_scraped_from":"https://www.freejobalert.com/articles/rajasthan-anganwadi-recruitment-2026-bharatpur-apply-offline-for-55-anganwadi-worker-and-helper-posts-3058745","slug":"rajasthan-anganwadi-recruitment-2026-bharatpur-apply-offline-for-55-anganwadi","category":"10TH_Pass"}